CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page A20, reads: "The Restland Lincoln Memorial Park booth was well represented by Euthlaw Blair, Agnes Williams, N.R. Conn, Ronald D. McDaniel, William F. Hayward, Thomas Logan, Connie Nash, James C. Rago, and Darwin Taylor."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: Euthlaw Blair, Agnes Williams, N.R. Conn, Ronald D. McDaniel, William F. Hayward, Thomas Logan, Connie Nash, James C. Rago, and Darwin Taylor, posed in Restland-Lincoln Memorial Park booth in Syria Mosque for the 1956 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
